author: akarasulu
msg: Fixed the race condition beteen entry responses and the done response on
search requests.  We no longer just wait half a second.  All entry
response sends for the same request are sent one at a time synchronously
then the done reponse for the search is sent asynchronously.  These
synchronous pathways are possible through a new synchronous method exposed
on the Encoder and the OutputManager.
